short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides access to certain OS OpenData products within the WME environment

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension for the Waze Map Editor, provides streetname suggestions pulled from the OS OpenData database, and allows selected third-party mapping sites to be opened up at the same location as the WME map.
